t worth buyers. NFT buyers can participate to collect and/or participate within the issuers'' ecosystem and metaverse. We expect a very diverse array of projects from games, collectibles, high-quality artwork with built-in economies to decentralized applications, and infrastructure projects.\n\nThe LaceUp launchpad ecosystem consists of two primary participants:\n\n*Project and NFT Issuer*\n\nProjects work closely with the Lovelace team to conceptualize, create, and issue their NFTs on LaceUp. NFTs sales may be linked to airdropped project tokens, unlock special functionality, enhance gaming, provide gamified yields, and/or provide unique experiences to their holders.\n\n*NFT Purchaser*\n\nNFT Purchasers buy NFTs listed on LaceUp and hold them within their wallets to gain access to airdropped tokens, unlock special functionality, earn gamified yields and/or receive unique experiences within a projects metaverse.\n\nThe LaceUp launchpad serves as a destination for the release of both third-party developed as well as in-house Lovelace projects.\n\n  \n\nLEARN MORE ABOUT LOVELACE WORLD\n\nWebsite and Social Media:\n\nWebsite: https://lovelace.world/\n\nTwitter (83k+ followers): https://twitter.com/LovelaceWorld\n\nDiscord (12k+ followers): https://discord.com/invite/6w49dSAd5M\n\nTelegram (32k+ followers): https://t.me/lovelaceofficial\n\nSelect Media Coverage:\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8P4yWlvV9PI\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QLrZ0B81vjg\n\nThank you for your consideration! We look forward to serving creators and the Cardano community with your support.", "importance": "GameFi & metaverse building is taking the industry by storm. We need to have a funding\u00a0vehicle to attract projects to build on Cardano.", "goal": "A decentralized treasury will give projects incentives to build GameFi on Cardano and allow the community to decide what interests them.", "metrics": "*   Amount of new users attracted to the Cardano metaverse from outside ecosystems\n*  